HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta ce an samu karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta ce yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
Kwararrun likitoci sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar.
A cikin shekara ta 2018 kawai, an yi rahoton cewa an yi sabon kamuwa da cutar a kashi 40,000 na shekara ta biyu.
Yawancin sababbin abubuwa sun faru ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nufin cewa an canja yanayin fiye da dā.
A tarihi, cutar HIV ta yi yawa a wurare da yawa a ƙasar Sin saboda jini da aka yi amfani da shi.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV a wannan lokacin ya ragu sosai, in ji jami'an lafiya a ƙasar Sin a wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Ana yin yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i a cikin al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
