Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a birnin Palu da ke ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Alhamis, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ƙaru.
Da yake an daina samun isashen bayanai, jami'an tsaro sun kasa samun bayanai daga ofishin da ke kula da birnin Donggala, inda girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 ta auku.
A ƙasar Pallu, an ceci mutane fiye da 16,000 daga wurin da aka yi hatsarin.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da birnin Palu da Donggala da ke birnin Sulawesi:
Palau babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, kuma a ƙarshen wani karamin tsibiri ne a yammacin tekun Sulawesi, kuma a shekara ta 2017 akwai mazauna 379,800.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami, birnin yana cika shekara 40 da aka yi hakan.
Ƙasar tana da nisan mil 180 a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A shekarar 2017, birnin da ke yankin, da ke karkashin gwamnatin jihar, ya kai kimanin mutane 299,200.
Kasashen Sulawesi suna da ci gaba sosai a fannin kamun kifi da kuma noma, musamman a yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Wani muhimmin abu kuma da ake samu a yankin shi ne dutsen nickel, amma ana samunsa a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an kai wa birnin Palu da Donggala hari da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya sake fashewa a yammacin birnin Donggala kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
A cikin tekun Pacific, ƙasar Indonesia tana da girgije da ke cike da girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya-bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a gabashin tekun Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indoneshiya kuma ta afku da tsunami a ƙasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabashin Tekun Indiya.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris, a watan Maris, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a yammacin Sumatra.
Ƙari ga haka, an kashe ɗarurruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wani tsunami da aka yi a yammacin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan mutane a ƙasar Indonesia, ya kai ga mutuwar mutane 700 a wani yanki da ke kudu maso yamma.
A shekara ta 2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afka wa wani gari kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
A shekara ta 2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa wani tsibiri a jihar Mentawai da ke Sumatra.
2016: Wani ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ya afka wa birnin Aceh da ke birnin Pidie Jaya kuma hakan ya sa mutane su ji tsoro sosai don abin da ya faru a shekara ta 2004 da kuma tsunami da suka yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane da yawa.
Babu tsunami da ya faru, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 a cikin guguwar.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa ta yi girgizar tsibirin Lombok a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma mutane fiye da 500 suka mutu.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gidaje kuma ta bar baƙi a cikin gidaje.
