Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da tashin hankali a birnin NYC
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York sun bukaci a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York - hukuncin da jihar ta ba da a kan tuhumar tarayya tun shekara ta 1953.
An zargi Saipov, ɗan shekara 30, da cewa ya yi amfani da motar da aka haya ta Home Depot don ya kai hari a kan hanyar babura a West Side da ke Lower Manhattan, kuma ya buge masu tafiya da kuma kekuna a kan hanyar.
Don a tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu shigar da kara sun bukaci su ba da hujja cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi musu rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a Jihar New York ta Kudu.
An yanke wa waɗannan 'yan'uwan hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin takardun kotu.
Bayan makonni da yawa bayan harin, sai wani babban alkalin kotun tarayya ya tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka guda 22 da suka haɗa da kisan kai da ake yi a wasu wurare, da kuma kashe mutane takwas da ake tuhumar da su a lokacin da ake tuhumarsu da kuma lalata mota.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce, wannan harin ya bukaci "shirya da kuma tunani sosai", kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata wannan "matsalolin da suka fi muni".
"Aikin Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo raunin da haɗari, da kuma asarar iyalan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar da aka yi game da shirin.
Biyar daga cikin mutanen da aka kai wa hari 'yan ƙasar Argentina ne.
Shekaru goma da suka shige, ne ƙaramar kotu da ta yanke hukunci a kan wani laifi na kisa a jihar New York.
An tuhumi Khalid Barnes da laifin kashe 'yan kasuwa biyu da ke sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi, amma a watan Nuwamba na shekara ta 2009 aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku.
A shekara ta 1953, an yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe a birnin New York.
An kashe Rosenberg a kan kujera a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Wani mai aikin binne gawa mai suna Saipov a ƙasar Uzbekistan ya ce bai tuba ba game da abin da ya yi a kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ta gaya wa 'yan sanda cewa ta ji daɗin abin da ta yi.
Saipov ya ce ya soma son yin kisan kai bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, kamar yadda takardun farko suka nuna.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya sake neman a saka tutar IS a ɗakinsa.
Ya ƙi amincewa da zarginsa guda 22 a cikin waɗannan takardun.
Wani mai suna David Patton, wanda ya yi aiki a matsayin mai kāre gwamnatin tarayya a birnin Saipov, ya ce sun "yi baƙin ciki ƙwarai" da aka yanke shawarar tuhumarsu.
Patton ya ce: "Mun yi imani cewa hukuncin kisa maimakon a ɗaure shi a kurkuku ba tare da an sake shi ba zai sa dukan waɗanda suka yi wannan laifin baƙin ciki sosai".
Da farko, 'yan sandan da ke kāre Saipov sun roƙi masu gabatar da kara su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisar Tory sun ce NIGEL FARAGE ne zai jagoranci tattaunawar neman da kuma tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawari cewa zai 'ƙulla yaƙi da mutane' a yau a lokacin taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban kungiyar ta Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su ji 'zafin' 'yan kungiyar Eurosceptics - kamar yadda ɗaya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ta ce ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar neman amincewa da kuma shawarwari na EU.
Wani mai goyon bayan jam'iyyar Conservative mai suna Peter Bone ya gaya wa taron a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta iya 'fita' yanzu da Mista Farage da kuma Sakataren Brexit.
Amma ƙalubalen da Mrs. May ta fuskanta wajen haɗa ikilisiyarta da ke da rabuwa da juna ya kasance ne saboda masu goyon bayan Tories da suka shiga zanga-zangar ta musamman da ke adawa da Brexit.
Firayim Minista yana da matsala sosai wajen kiyaye tsarin Chequers da aka kafa a kusurwarsa a cikin harin da 'yan asalin Brexit suka kai, tunatarwa a cikin EU.
Allies ta nace cewa za ta ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da cewa za a yi ta daɗi - kuma ta tilasta wa 'yan sandan da ke da ra'ayin rashin amincewa da tsarin da ake kira Eurosceptics da kuma Ma'aikata su zaɓi tsakanin yarjejeniyar da ta yi da kuma 'rashin jituwa.'
Mista Bone ya gaya wa wata kungiya mai suna Leave Means Leave a garin Solihull cewa yana son ya 'karya 'yan Chequers.'
Ya ce za a yi wa Farage aiki a matsayin abokin tarayya kuma ya ba shi aikin tuntuɓar da kuma tuntuɓar da'irar a birnin Brussels.
Ya ce: 'Da shi ne shugaban, da mun bar wurin yanzu.
Wani ɗan majalisar dokokin garin Wellingborough ya ce: 'Zan yi goyon bayan Brexit amma dole ne mu yi watsi da Jam'iyyar Chequers.'
Ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙi ba don mu sami 'yanci.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayoyin da ke nuna cewa yanayin al'umma ya canja tun bayan zaben 2016, ya ce: 'Ba gaskiya ba ne cewa mutanen Biritaniya sun canja ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su ci gaba da zama a ƙasar.'
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma yana wurin taron, ya gaya wa manema labarai: "Na ce, Firayim Minista, ka saurari mutane.
'Yan takara da ba su da suna a ƙasar, 'Yan adawa da 'yan siyasa, suna iya jefa ƙuri'a a kansu, kuma ba mu saba ganin yadda ake samun su a kan titi ba.
Ka daina zama ɗan Chequers kuma ka soma sauraro.'
A cikin saƙon da aka aika wa Misis May, ta ƙara da cewa: 'Shugabannin gwamnati suna riƙe da aikinsu kuma suna cika alkawarinsu.'
Mista Farage ya gaya wa 'yan siyasa na garin cewa ya kamata a 'yi musu zafi' idan sun kusa cin amanar da aka yanke a taron jama'a na 2016.
Ya ce: "Wannan ya shafi dangantakarmu da 'yan siyasa.
'Suna son su yi nasara a kan Brexit kuma a yau sun zo ne don su gaya musu cewa 'ba za mu bar ku ku yi nasara ba.'
Ya daɗa cewa: 'Ina son ku sa 'yan siyasa da ke kan hamadar cin amanar Brexit su ji daɗin wannan taron.
'Muna da yakin da mutanen ƙasar suka yi mana da ya sa muka yi nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama 'yancin kai, masu ɗabi'a, da kuma girman kai na Burtaniya.'
A lokacin, 'yan bindiga sun bi ta Birmingham kafin su yi awa biyu suna tafiya a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan ta'addan sun yi watsi da 'yan Tories da suka yi hamayya da Brexit bayan da aka gabatar da wannan jam'iyyar a karshen mako.
Abokin aikinsa na 'yan Sanda, Lord Adonis, ya yi wa 'yan majalisa ba'a game da batun tsaro da suka fuskanta a lokacin da aka buɗe taron.
Ya kara da cewa: "Waɗannan mutane ne suka gaya mana cewa za su iya yin wannan aikin IT a shirye tare da dukan masu fasaha na Kanada da kuma, game da iyakar da ba ta da rikici, game da cinikayya ta kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland".
'Wannan wasan ne mai kyau.
