Shugaba Donald Trump ya nuna wa Sanata Dianne Feinstein a ranar Asabar cewa ta nace cewa ba ta karya wasiƙar da Christine Blasey Ford ta rubuta ba, wadda ta zargi dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da lalata.
A jawabinsa a wani kotun da ke yammacin Virginia, shugaban ya yi watsi da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa, kuma a matsayinsa ya ce abin da ya faru a jihar ya nuna cewa mutane "masu mugunta ne, marasa adalci kuma ba sa gaskiya".
Ya ce: "Abin da ya fi kyau a cikin kwanaki na ƙarshe na wannan shekara shi ne ganin mutane da suke fushi da kuma nuna rashin gaskiya".
"Idan ka kalli hoton da aka yi da kuma abin da aka yi da shi, sai ka ce, 'Ban yi hakan ba.
Ban taɓa yin hakan ba".
Ka tuna?
Dianne Feinstein, ba ta da hankali?
Ka tuna da yadda ya yi magana da shi.
A'a, ba haka ba ne.
Ban taɓa yin hakan ba".
A wannan yanayin, ka jira na minti ɗaya.
"Ba mu da ƙanshi", in ji shi, yana daɗa da ƙanshi.
A watan Yuli, an aika wa Feinstein da wasiƙa da ta bayyana zargin da Ford ya yi wa Kavanaugh, kuma an sare shi a farkon watan Satumba.
Jaridar The Hill ta ruwaito cewa, Feinstein ya gaya wa kwamitin cewa: "Ban ɓoye zargin da Dr. Ford ya yi mini ba, ban yi kome ba".
Ya ce: "Ya ce in tsare shi, kuma na yi hakan".
Amma shugaban ya yi fushi sosai da hakan, kuma ya ce a wani jawabi da aka yi a garin Mgcibeo da dare: "Na gaya maka, wannan baƙar magana ce.
Wataƙila ba ya yin hakan, amma harshe ne mai banƙyama da ban taɓa gani ba".
Da yake ci gaba da kare kansa daga takarar Kotun Koli, wanda aka zargi mata uku da lalata, shugaban ya ce 'yan Democrat sun yi amfani da zargin don cimma burinsu.
"Suna son su dawo da ƙarfinsu ta hanyar da ta dace.
Ya ga irin wannan mugunta da rashin adalci da suke yi, ba sa son su ji wa kowa rauni, kuma ba sa son su sami iko da iko".
Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 da Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci raga biyu a raga a kan Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi hasarar Elite League a ranar Alhamis a kan Belfast Giants ta hanyar cin nasara 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
A lokacin, 'yan Giants sun ci kwallo biyu da sauri ta hanyar buga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kawo matakin gida kafin Dwyer ya dawo da shugabancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya yi daidai da Dundee kafin Luka Lundvald Nielsen ya ci nasara.
Wannan ne nasara ta uku da Adam Keefe ya yi a gasar Premier a wannan kakar, wanda ya ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a daren Alhamis.
Wannan ne karo na huɗu da aka yi a wannan kakar wasan da ƙungiyoyin biyu suka yi, inda Giants suka ci wasanni uku da suka gabata.
