Amma, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi nasara a wasan, za ta yi amfani da ita sosai don ta rage yawan kuɗin da ake kashewa.
Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike a Asiya a New American Security Center, ta ce: "Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa da aka yi a Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da canje-canje a tattalin arziki a ƙasarsu ya fi haɗari fiye da abin da masu kallo suka gani a dā".
